HEADWORD: Confirmatory
<hw>Con*firm"a*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Serving to
confirm; corroborative.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A fact <qex>confirmatory</qex> of the conclusion.</q> <rj><qau>I.
